kz\_indiana\_jumps
==================

A little longjump training map, containing a longjump, weirdjump and ladderjump. It also features a little climb part for you guys to mess around a little bit. 

Also has one secret and an ending song, when finishing the climb.

Originally made for the bhop.it servers.

### BHOP.IT BUNNYHOP    94.75.251.224:27017

### BHOP.IT LONGJUMP    94.75.251.224:27016
